    "Sentiment can also be expressed implicitly, requiring deeper semantic understanding.",
    "The health domain introduces unique linguistic challenges.",
    "It possesses a specialized vocabulary, including medical jargon, acronyms, and informal patient terms (e.g., \"brain fog\") that general-purpose NLP tools may not understand (29).",
